AV_GET_CBO_NCIC_TRANSPORT_MAKE.definition:
CREATE     VIEW [dbo].[AV_GET_CBO_NCIC_TRANSPORT_MAKE] AS
SELECT NcicTransportMakeId,
       TransportTypeId,
       Description,
       NcicCode,
       Comments,
	   Active
FROM   DUI.TBL_OPT_NCIC_Transport_Make
UNION
SELECT NcicTransportMakeId           = 0,
       TransportTypeId = TBL_OPT_NCIC_Transport_Type.NcicTransportTypeId,
       Description       = '',
       NcicCode         = '',
       Comments          = '',
	   Active
FROM   DUI.TBL_OPT_NCIC_Transport_Type
UNION
SELECT NcicTransportMakeId           = 0,
       TransportTypeId = 0,
       Description       = '',
       NcicCode         = '',
       Comments          = '',
	   1 AS Active
